Want to be able to hot swap a class after, say, method addition/removal? This is a plugin for you then!

This is an IntelliJ IDEA plugin which provides integration with <a href="http://ssw.jku.at/dcevm/">DCEVM</a> - an OpenJDK-based JVM
which fixes standard <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hot_swapping">java HotSwap</a>.